WinDiv window resizing utility
==============================
Simple tool to resize a window with a grid.

To Run:
Build and double click on WinDiv.exe.
Click the window you would like to resize and hit the global hotkey Alt+F1 to bring up the resizing window.
Click and drag mouse across grid to get the desired size. Let go of the mouse button and the window will be resized.
Hit Escape to close resizing window.
To close the application, right click on grid icon in the system tray and choose exit.